In WorkflowRunner

Bij parallel scenario:

public List<String> findExecutableNodes(
        GraphModel graph,
        Map<String, NodeExecutionStatus> statuses
) {
    return graph.nodes().keySet().stream()
            .filter(nodeId -> statuses.get(nodeId) == null)
            .filter(nodeId -> graph.predecessors(nodeId).stream()
                    .allMatch(pred -> statuses.get(pred) == NodeExecutionStatus.SUCCEEDED))
            .toList();
}

Voor MVP kun je dit nog simpel houden, maar dit is al future-proof.

